    "response_text": "The commercial opens on a black frame, then cuts to a close-up of a white circular badge pinned to orange fabric. The badge reads, in decorative script, “Come fly with me...”.\n\nIt then moves into a fast montage of travel- and leisure-related images:\n\n- A hand points with a pen or pointer at large maps or charts spread across a desk.\n- A low-angle shot shows a uniformed man in a light-blue shirt and cap, raising his hands near what appears to be an aircraft.\n- The Statue of Liberty is shown from above or at an elevated angle, with water and city structures in the background.\n- A close-up shows a smiling blonde woman wearing an orange cap or hat.\n- A man in a dark suit appears indoors, partially blurred by motion or soft focus.\n- A tennis player in white is seen mid-action on a court near tall buildings.\n- A blurred outdoor scene follows, with figures and movement, but the activity is not clearly visible.\n- Two men in suits sit indoors; an orange balloon or round object with “Come fly with me” is visible in front of them.\n- A group of people appear seated together outdoors or in an open vehicle; the image is soft and fast-moving.\n- Silhouetted people stand or sit near tall windows, one holding or standing beside a pale round object.\n- A brief abstract or transitional shot shows vertical architectural forms and an orange circular object near the bottom.\n\nThe montage then shows service and recreation scenes:\n\n- A woman in a colorful uniform serves drinks from a tray, holding a metal coffee pot and cups toward a seated person.\n- Two people sit in a small blue rowboat; one holds an oar.\n- A person navigates rough white water, possibly in a kayak or small craft.\n- The white “Come fly with me...” badge reappears in close-up.\n- The badge image dissolves over a close-up of the smiling woman in the orange cap.\n\nThe commercial then features uniformed personnel and more travel imagery:\n\n- A uniformed man in a cap stands in a covered area with strong horizontal ceiling lines behind him.\n- Large text appears across plain backgrounds in separate shots: “Come,” a stylized “fly,” and “me...”.\n- The circular “Come fly with me...” badge appears again, now with warmer brown/gold lettering.\n- The smiling woman in the orange cap is shown wearing a round badge on her chest.\n- A smiling uniformed man in a blue shirt and tie is shown with a similar round badge.\n- Another low-angle shot shows the light-blue-uniformed man with a headset and patches on his shirt.\n- A fast, dark outdoor shot shows several people moving together; the exact activity is unclear.\n- Two people ride horses against a bright blue sky and distant landscape.\n- The word “with” appears in large blue lettering on a pale background.\n\nThe final frame shows an airplane flying above clouds or a blue aerial landscape. Large white text over the image reads: “fly the friendly skies of United.”"
